snippet.title: LimboGameplay
snippet.description:
This is a developers play through of the first boss in The Devil's Eight, Limbo. This is still prealpha footage, the final experience will have additional attacks, improved animations, better sound effects , and more.  

The Devil's Eight is currently on Kickstarter:
https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/928406908/the-devils-eight-stylish-music-driven-boss-rush
